OL,3,CHospital urges parents to vaccinate
OL,4,Cafter reports a child died from measles
OL,6,FAlder Hey Children's Hospital has
OL,7,Furged parents to vaccinate their
OL,8,Fchildren after reports of a child in
OL,9,FLiverpool dying due to contracting
OL,10,Fmeasles.
OL,12,FThe child is believed to be the second
OL,13,Fto succumb to an acute measles
OL,14,Finfection in Britain in the last
OL,15,Fdecade, according to The Sunday Times
OL,16,Fnewspaper.
OL,18,FThe hospital said it couldn't comment
OL,19,Fon individual cases, but warned of a
OL,20,Frise in measles cases and urged
OL,21,Ffamilies to get vaccinated.
