OL,3,CHospital urges parents to vaccinate
OL,4,Cafter reports a child died from measles
OL,6,FMeasles is highly contagious and can
OL,7,Fcause serious illness, especially in
OL,8,Fchildren with weaker immune systems.
OL,9,FIn rare cases, it can be fatal.
OL,11,FThe warning comes as vaccination rates
OL,12,Fin the UK continue to fall.
OL,14,FA recent report by the Royal College
OL,15,Fof Paediatrics and Child Health
OL,16,F(RCPCH) found that no routine
OL,17,Fchildhood vaccine has met the 95%
OL,18,Fuptake target since 2021, leaving many
OL,19,Fchildren at risk from illnesses like
OL,20,Fmeasles, whooping cough and meningitis.
